

Adding a product: (POST)
http://localhost/api/products/add.php

{
	"price": 10,
	"productType": "socks",
	"color": "yellow",
	"size": "L"
}

{
	"price": 30,
	"productType": "hoodie",
	"color": "black",
	"size": "M"
}

{
	"price": 20,
	"productType": "t-shirt",
	"color": "white",
	"size": "XL"
}

-----------------------------------------------------------------

View all products (GET)
http://localhost/api/products/products.php

View one product
http://localhost/api/products/product.php?id=1

-----------------------------------------------------------------

Adding an order: (POST)
http://localhost/api/products/create-order.php

(product ID) : (quantity)
{
	"1": "2",
	"2": "2"
}

Viewing orders (GET)
http://localhost/api/products/view-orders.php

Viewing orders that contain item of a specific type (GET)
http://localhost/api/products/view-orders.php?type=socks
